Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:39.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95908,99037}– See you later!\N– Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:43.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102081,103750}Hey, Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106169,108421}Are you looking for UFOs again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108421,110173}You don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:51.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110173,111799}That's my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:55.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111799,115720}We're in the fifth grade now.\NIt's time you gave it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116262,118806}Why? UFOs really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118806,120933}How can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120933,122560}– Sure they do!\N– They don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:03.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122560,123770}– Do!\N– Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:06.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123770,126939}– If I say they do, they do!\N– Show me some proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126939,129400}Right, proof. The proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:13.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129817,133780}Proof, proof, proof, proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133780,135073}I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135073,136449}You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:19.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136449,139827}I'll show you for sure! For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:25.83,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141663,145833}The U.F.O. Appears!?\NA Town in Panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:27.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146376,147835}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148419,150254}Good morning, Ryoko, Kyoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150254,152590}You saw the UFO last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152590,154050}UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:36.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154050,156761}The one in the morning paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157053,159931}Meimi, don't you read the papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159931,161974}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:47.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162433,167021}A UFO?\N"Several eyewitnesses in Seika City".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:50.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167021,170942}It says people saw\Na shiny object flying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170942,172985}That's definitely a UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172985,175071}But why the city of Seika?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175071,178074}What else?\NIt's because St. Tail is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179492,182036}St. Tail is probably\Na messenger from outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:07.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184288,187500}Yeah, a thief who roams\Nthe universe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:11.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189669,191462}How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191796,194090}Who says she's a messenger\Nfrom outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:15.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194090,195800}What a terrible way to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195800,198928}There's no such thing as aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199178,201013}Then what's this article about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201013,202932}An optical illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:27.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203599,207979}It says many people saw it.\NCan you still call it an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:31.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207979,211607}An airplane, a shooting star…\NAnyway, something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211607,213860}UFOs aren't scientific!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213860,216863}Science has yet\Nto prove many things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216863,220408}– Miss Haneoka, Mr. Asuka.\N– Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:44.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220700,224871}The two of you, use that energy\Nand go do your science homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225538,226873}Yes, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:58.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234922,238301}Haneoka!\NHave you heard about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239093,240261}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:05.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241179,245224}"From the space shuttle to UFOs.\NCosmo World."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:10.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245808,250688}"Popular event producer Yuji Kuroda\Nturns the Big Dome into outer space."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251147,254484}The UFO in the papers,\Na guy took a photo of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254484,256152}Wow! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:20.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256694,260156}And that photo will be exhibited\Nat this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260156,263117}You're saying you wanna\Ngo and see it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263409,265077}Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:29.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265077,269582}If I see it, I'll know if it's real or not.\NAnd tomorrow's Sunday…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:33.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270917,273961}Good idea.\NLet's go and check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273961,275671}Well, now, is this a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275671,278049}Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281886,284388}Okay, we're ready. Go get Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284388,286182}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286182,287850}Dad, dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287850,289018}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289018,291103}Is he outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:59.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295608,299028}That's strange. No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299529,300780}Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303616,305493}Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:08.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305910,308788}Wow! It's a new magic trick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:14.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310039,314460}This is much thinner than the piano\Ncord I used. Can't see it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316045,319423}Ruby, don't struggle.\NDon't struggle so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:25.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322385,325263}Is she all right? Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:28.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325263,328099}Looks like the reeling mechanism\Nneeds more work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330101,331894}Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:44.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340111,344824}{\i1}I said that to Seira,\Nbut this is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:46.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344824,346367}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346367,347743}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348661,350037}It's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:53.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350037,353958}What's with the sour face?\NSorry we're not Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355626,358337}Ryoko, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358337,360840}We heard about it, how it's a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360840,362216}Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362216,364093}Can we come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:06.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364093,366429}Well, sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368431,370433}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370766,373144}You guys came along too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373144,375605}This has to be enjoyed together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375605,376981}Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377940,380359}I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:32.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390578,392997}Not very many people are in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:38.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392997,398044}This model is also cheaply made.\NThere's no detail whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398044,400004}Where's Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400421,403090}Now that you mention it…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403090,404967}Maybe he's stuck to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408804,410723}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410723,412433}Hey, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412934,414936}Let's take a look at the UFO photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415353,416312}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424236,425488}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:08.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425488,428783}"The photos are being enlarged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:13.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428783,433037}They will be shown on the last day\Nat the UFO summoning event."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433537,437375}There, you see? It's a fake\Nso they're delaying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:21.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437375,441504}No, they're probably having\Nan expert examine the photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441504,444423}I'll go ask someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444840,446384}Mr. Kuroda, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447093,450888}You're not drawing a crowd.\NAt this rate, we'll be in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:36.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450888,456227}Don't worry, a turnout will come on\Nthe last day. No one will miss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456227,458062}You mean that UFO photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:43.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458562,463776}Yes, it's fabulous. It's the hottest\Nconversation piece in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:48.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464193,468739}But shouldn't an expert examine it\Nbefore you show it to the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:53.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469490,473703}By the time we do that, the event\Nwill be over. It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473703,475121}But still…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475121,478165}My job is to gather people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:03.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478165,483379}I've planned, along with the photo,\Nan event to summon a real UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:06.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483379,486257}It'll be a smash hit, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487675,489719}Anyway, we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489719,491012}Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496559,498144}{\i1}It's the man in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:24.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498728,504734}But, sir, if we enlarge the photo,\Neveryone will know that it's a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505192,507028}Stupid fool! You're talking too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508696,510906}Hey, Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:35.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510906,515703}Why are you hanging around here?\NHurry up so we can see the UFO—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517621,518581}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518581,520750}You're the one who stepped on—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:43.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520750,523753}The UFO model's that way.\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523753,525880}Kids nowadays are too mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526547,528382}{\i1}Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:54.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531510,534305}You're talking about the UFO\Nin the papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:59.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534847,539602}Yeah. I want to see a UFO so badly,\NI always carry a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539602,543647}But because of that,\Nmy friends make fun of me, so I…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560790,562833}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:30.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566003,570299}– Wow!\N– That's neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570925,572885}Is this some sort of hoax?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:37.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572885,577056}It's real.\NIt was even in this morning's paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577056,578599}It's probably the same UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578599,580851}Shota, you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580851,582812}Sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582812,585731}Then it was just\Na remote control airplane?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:50.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586357,590486}Yeah. I didn't expect it\Nto become such a big sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:56.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591487,596408}And then my friends took the photo\Nto Cosmo World without me knowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:57.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596826,597743}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:01.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597743,601330}And it's going to be\Nexhibited at that event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601330,603249}Have you asked for the photo back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603249,604750}Yes, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604750,605793}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:13.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608796,613300}My friends brought it in without\Nmy permission, that UFO photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613634,615469}Oh, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:20.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615469,620266}It's just the thing for this event,\Nso we're putting it on exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:25.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621350,625729}I'm sorry. It's a fake.\NSo please return it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:30.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626730,630693}Too late now. We already advertised\Nthat it'll be on exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631110,632194}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:37.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633529,637908}You better not tell anyone\Nit's a fake. They'll never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638242,641620}That's unfair. Please return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:45.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642288,645124}I'll return it to you\Nwhen the event is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649295,651839}If only I hadn't taken that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:57.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652423,657303}I understand. Let's pray.\NI'm sure God is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657887,660806}I see. So that's the story\Nbehind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:06.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661390,666270}Shota regrets what he has done\Nand promises not to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:11.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667021,671692}Okay! The thief St. Tail shall get\Nthat photo back for him.
Comment: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:11.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:671692,671692}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:17.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:677698,677698}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:22.70,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:682703,682703}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710439,711273}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:55.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711273,715277}"Tonight I'll be stealing\Nthat UFO photo at the Big Dome."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716237,717488}St. Tail…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:09.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726956,729833}St. Tail is after that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:14.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730209,734672}Yes, so we'll be taking care\Nof the security for the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734672,736298}I can use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:22.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737216,742263}I thought that if we could get a photo\Nto reveal St. Tail's identity…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742763,744765}What would you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:29.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744765,749895}An event, of course. With that photo,\Ncrowds will swarm to such an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749895,752982}Absolutely not! To make\NSt. Tail into such a spectacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754775,757736}Well, I'll leave the security to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:41.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757736,761198}The photograph is set\Nin that slide projector over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763409,765411}Weren't you having it enlarged?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:49.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766245,769373}There are limits\Nto enlarging a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:53.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769373,773252}We're going to project it\Non a slide, like, bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:56.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773252,776422}Well, I've got things to prepare\Nso I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:02.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778590,782469}{\i1}Who's gonna let a guy like that\Nreveal St. Tail's identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:11.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787599,791437}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796483,797443}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799737,801113}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803115,805617}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:44.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820841,824386}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:54.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831643,834605}Ladies and gentlemen,\Nwelcome to Cosmo World!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:59.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835147,839943}All of you here tonight will\Nwitness a historical event!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:04.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839943,844656}The boy who took the photo we'll\Nbe showing had these words to say:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844990,848118}"The UFO will definitely return\Nto retrieve this photo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850621,851914}There's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:17.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851914,857169}We've been informed that St. Tail\Nmight appear to steal this photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:21.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857169,861340}Ladies and gentlemen,\Nhave you brought your cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861799,864301}What scum, saying a thing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:29.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864927,869431}For those who photograph a UFO\Nor St. Tail's true identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:32.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869431,872434}we have big rewards prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872434,874603}Now, let us begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:49.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886240,889284}Mr. Kuroda, there aren't\Nany rewards prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:55.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890119,895624}It'll be hard for anyone to photograph\NSt. Tail's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895624,898043}But what if someone\Ndoes photograph her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898752,900712}I'll buy it in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:04.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900712,904508}If we have that, I'll surely be able\Nto fill the Big Dome unlike before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905843,907344}But what about the UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:10.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907344,910973}Don't get your hopes up on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:15.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910973,915436}Didn't you say that a UFO\Nwill come to retrieve the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:21.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915436,921442}Just an act to arouse the audience.\NAnd that photo, it looks like a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921900,925821}That's a problem!\NLet's cancel the event right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925821,927406}Hey, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927823,931577}The only one who will be criticized\Nis the boy who took the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931577,934413}We're only victims of a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:39.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934413,939084}And luck is on our side\Nif a crowd gathers, am I not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939084,940627}How can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:48.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945257,948010}Mommy, when is the UFO coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948010,949011}I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949011,950971}It won't come, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950971,952097}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952639,955058}– Hurry up and summon the UFO!\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:57.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955517,957144}This is where we end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:04.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958770,964359}It looks like our UFO has decided\Nto make a sidetrack somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:09.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964860,969990}While we're waiting for its arrival,\Nwe'll present the UFO photo—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969990,971241}It's the UFO!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972409,974786}The UFO appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980918,982711}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983378,986089}Could it be a real UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989218,991678}It's St. Tail! After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991678,994264}Everyone! St. Tail has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994640,996725}– What?\N– St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997267,998227}Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998685,1000729}Hurry up and turn on the lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001396,1004733}No good!\NThe switch won't connect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004733,1005692}Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006068,1007361}There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007945,1009112}She's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009571,1010697}Don't let her escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015494,1016870}Are you all right, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016870,1018997}Never mind me, get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019873,1021124}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022834,1024127}There she is! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025671,1027089}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029841,1031093}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038433,1040978}St. Tail! This is where\Nthe chase ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043063,1045065}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045065,1046733}I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:29.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046733,1049111}The flash won't reach\Nfrom this far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050362,1052197}{\i1}This is just fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:37.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052197,1057786}Mr. Kuroda! This is big trouble!\NA UFO has really appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:42.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058370,1062749}What are you gonna do?\NYou know there aren't any rewards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063125,1064251}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064543,1065252}{\i1}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072593,1073552}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:59.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074344,1079057}Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:04.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083020,1084855}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:24.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100495,1104750}Well, Asuka Jr., I'll be\Nleaving with the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105250,1106752}Darn! Don't think\NI'll let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108503,1110881}Stop it! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110881,1112549}I won't let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112549,1114551}I can't stand this, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115719,1118138}No, it's not like this!\NI'm not a—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118138,1120223}Never mind!\NJust let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126396,1127689}Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134571,1135656}Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:00.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137741,1140786}That hurts. I shouldn't use\Nexperimental devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140786,1142120}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143747,1145332}Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145832,1147626}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:15.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150545,1155258}– Open this door! I've taken a picture!\N– Give me my reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:21.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158887,1161098}What is your plan now, Kuroda?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161098,1162849}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162849,1164685}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177614,1180784}"Hope you get a picture\Nof a real UFO next time."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182369,1183412}Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186998,1190210}How did you get that photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190210,1191837}It fell from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191837,1193296}From the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:55.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194840,1195924}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196675,1199010}It's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:02.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199010,1202931}I was in trouble, because they forced me\Nto have it revealed at the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204057,1205016}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:06.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205016,1206768}{\i1}So that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206768,1208437}{\i1}St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213567,1215610}Good morning, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215610,1216403}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216403,1219197}There was another UFO\Nappearance, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:23.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219197,1223952}That was just one of St. Tail's tricks.\NUFOs don't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223952,1226705}You still don't believe?\NYou're stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226705,1229750}In the first place,\Nanti-scientific things—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230250,1232043}What is it? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232043,1233211}That.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237966,1239843}Was that a…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:40.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239843,1240927}UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240927,1242053}Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242053,1243138}Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:47.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245348,1247851}Wait!
